<p style="margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:34.5pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:13.5pt;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in;background:white"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;">2.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;">Click the</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;">&nbsp;<b>Wireless Settings</b>&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;">tab.<br />
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style="margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:34.5pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:13.5pt;
